Kooxda WHO waxay ku talineysaa in dadka caafimaad qaba ay xirtaan maaskaro oo keliya marka ay halis ugu jiraan sida dadka daryeela COVID-19, laakiin waxay ku dartay in xirashada maaskaro ay ka caawin karto dadka inay ka fogaadaan inay taabtaan wejiyadooda.
