b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku xidhan dusha sare ee unugyada (cellular membranes) ee sanbabada, xididdada dhiigga, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo mindhicirka.
ACE2 waxay faa'iido weyn u leedahay daaweynta cudurada wadnaha, maadaama ay xakameyso shaqada enzyme-ka angiotensin-II ee la xiriira iyadoo hoos u dhigeysa heerarka Ang (1-7) iyo kor u qaadista heerarka Ang (1-7). ACE2 waxay sidoo kale u shaqeysaa sida albaabada gudaha ee qaar ka mid ah coronavirus.
Enzyme-ka aadanaha waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 waa nooc ka mid ah enzyme-ka metalloenzyme-ka ah ee ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada endothelial iyo unugyada kale.
Badeecada ACE2 waxay leedahay N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C-terminal collectrin domain oo ah wareejinta amino acid ee kelyaha.
ACE2 waa borotiinka xuubka ee nooca I ee hal-marinka ah, oo leh domain firfircoon oo enzymatic ah oo ku dhaca dusha unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale.
Adeegga ka baxsan unugyada ee ACE2 waxaa ka soo saaray unugyo kale oo loo yaqaan sheddase, oo ka soo baxa borotiinka dhalaalaya ee wareegaya dhiigga, ugu dambeynna lagu saaraa kaadida.
ACE2 waxay ku jirtaa inta badan qaybaha jirka - ACE2 waxay ku xirantahay inta badan xuubka unugyada sambabada ee nooca II ee unugyada sambabada, unugyada xayawaanka ee mindhicirka, unugyada xayawaanka ee xididdada iyo xididdada iyo unugyada muruqyada jilicsan ee xididdada inta badan jirka.
