In kasta oo aan la ogeyn sida ay u fududahay in cudurku u faafo, laakiin sida caadiga ah qofku wuxuu faafiyaa laba ilaa saddex qof, sida laga soo xigtay Xarunta Yurub ee Ka Hortagga iyo Xakamaynta Cudurrada (ECDC).
